{"tid":1956844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白事當紅事辦，一掌都唔撚拍，香港社區基金又係藍底","createTime":"2020-04-03T12:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T13:22:55.000Z","uid":3513,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7fd2a1c50fabfae074da2889d6aa040094136640","tid":1956844,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T12:41:59.000Z","msg":"全英上下拍手為醫護打氣一幕感動全球，宣稱是非牟利機構的「香港社區基金」今日在報章及傳媒網站大賣廣告，呼籲巿民晚上8時到窗前或街上集體鼓掌最少1分鐘，為前線醫護打氣；專門幫港府塗脂抹粉的「香港品牌」亦在社交網站上為活動加持。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">《蘋果》調查發現，該基金背後是知名「奶粉」、曾任林鄭月娥特首競選辦副主任的信和集團副主席黃永光，</span></span>他不但力撐被指「倒錢落海」的明日大嶼計劃<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">，去年7月反送中期間亦公開撐警</span></span>。前線醫護怒轟撐政府組織惺惺作態，拍手行動無意義。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200403/A7ODEJWYEXG2PORM5VZKTALYEE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200403%2FA7ODEJWYEXG2PORM5VZKTALYEE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2Bh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=c37a0989\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200403%2FA7ODEJWYEXG2PORM5VZKTALYEE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=cbf26509\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200403/A7ODEJWYEXG2PORM5VZKTALYEE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢啲乜撚野基金 仲要咁疊水落足廣告 <br />\n你就知奶野啦</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal